{"componentChunkName":"component---src-layouts-blog-post-layout-js","path":"/blog/minimal-theme-slideshow-on-product-pages-tutorial","result":{"pageContext":{"id":618,"date":"2021-03-27T06:12:23","date_gmt":"2021-03-27T06:12:23","guid":{"rendered":"https://www.ezfy.club/?p=618"},"modified":"2021-03-27T06:55:27","modified_gmt":"2021-03-27T06:55:27","slug":"minimal-theme-slideshow-on-product-pages-tutorial","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https://www.ezfy.club/minimal-theme-slideshow-on-product-pages-tutorial/","title":{"rendered":"Minimal Theme: add a slideshow to your product pages"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>One of the best things about the minimal theme is its particularly elegant simplicity. However, in one specific area that its simplicity fails to deliver is at the product page; lacking a proper way to present images can be a deal breaker for the pickiest customers. Constantly clicking between thumbnails and then scrolling up to see the new image doesn&#8217;t feel like the most UX friendly approach.<br><br>In this tutorial I&#8217;ll show you how you can quick and easily add a slideshow to your Minimal theme product page, all it takes is copying and pasting one single code file. You can <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://acid-tests.myshopify.com/products/dummy-product\" target=\"_blank\">view the end result clicking here</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Making a backup of your current theme</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Before diving into the tutorial make sure you download the theme, so in case you face any issues you can easily revert back.<br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1514\" height=\"481\" class=\"wp-image-503\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123.png 1514w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-600x191.png 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-1200x381.png 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-768x244.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1514px) 100vw, 1514px\" /></p>\n\n\n\n<h3>How it works &amp; downloading the necessary code</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Download options:<br><br><s>Download the simple version clicking here (live preview) &#8211; password is: 123</s> <strong>(no longer available)</strong><br>Download the <strong>pro version</strong> clicking <a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/shop/minimal-theme-slider-pro\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">here</a>. (<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://acid-tests.myshopify.com/products/dummy-product\" target=\"_blank\">live preview</a>)<br><br>This code snippet creates extra options at the customize page of your theme.<br><br>Below, whichever options have (customizable) are options that you’ll be to enable, disable and/or customize in some way.<br><br>Here are all the current features:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table is-style-stripes\"><table><thead><tr><th class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Features </th><th class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">Pro</th><th class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">Simple</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Swipe featured image</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td></tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Featured image arrows (customizable &#8211; enable for desktop only, mobile only or both)</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"></td></tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Zoom on mouse hover️ (customizable)</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"></td></tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Zoom on mouse click &#8211; shows image on a lightbox/popup (customizable, works only for desktop)</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"></td></tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Swipe thumbnails</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"></td></tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Thumbnail arrows (enable for desktop only, mobile only or both)</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"></td></tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Choose how many thumbnails to show (3, 4, 5, 6 or use the default Minimal thumbnails without a slider)</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"></td></tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Highlighted thumbnail alignment (left, center or right)</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"></td></tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Thumbnail vertical alignment (top or center)</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"></td></tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Update featured image to its equivalent variant whenever changing a variant through the dropdown (works exclusively with dropdowns. If you&#8217;re using custom swatches or buttons to show variants this function may not work.)</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"></td></tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Update dropdown whenever changing an image to its equivalent variant (works exclusively with dropdowns. If you&#8217;re using custom swatches or buttons to show variants this function will not work.)</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"></td></tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Automatically updates the featured image if there is a variant on the URL&#8217;s query string</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"> ✔️</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"></td></tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Update dropdown variant whenever image is changed (customizable &#8211; works exclusively with dropdowns. If you&#8217;re using custom swatches or buttons to show variants this function will not work.)</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"></td></tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Lazyload to improve performance (customizable)</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"></td></tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Lifetime <strong>free </strong>updates</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"></td></tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Bug fixes</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"></td></tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Constantly maintained </td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"></td></tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">New features based on user feedback</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The complete details about the <strong>pro</strong> version <a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/shop/minimal-theme-slider-pro\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">can be found here</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Installing the slideshow code onto your theme</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>In your Shopify admin, navigate to&nbsp;<strong>Online Store</strong>&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Themes&nbsp;</strong>&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Actions&nbsp;</strong>&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Edit Code</strong>.<br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1349\" height=\"614\" class=\"wp-image-626\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/edit-code.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/edit-code.jpg 1349w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/edit-code-600x273.jpg 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/edit-code-1200x546.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/edit-code-768x350.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1349px) 100vw, 1349px\" /></li><li>Find a file named <strong>product-template.liquid</strong><br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1004\" height=\"417\" class=\"wp-image-628\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/product-template.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/product-template.jpg 1004w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/product-template-600x249.jpg 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/product-template-768x319.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1004px) 100vw, 1004px\" /></li><li>Delete everything inside of this file. Make sure it is blank:<br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1265\" height=\"548\" class=\"wp-image-630\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/blank1.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/blank1.jpg 1265w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/blank1-600x260.jpg 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/blank1-1200x520.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/blank1-768x333.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1265px) 100vw, 1265px\" /></li><li>Now, inside of the .zip you downloaded, there will be a file called <strong>product-template.txt</strong>. Copy all the code inside of this file.</li><li>Paste this code you copied into <strong>product-template.liquid</strong> and save.</li><li>That is it! Your slideshow is now working and ready to use.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<h3>Customizing your new slideshow to your liking</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>In your Shopify admin, navigate to&nbsp;<strong>Online Store</strong>&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Themes&nbsp;</strong>&gt;<strong>Customize</strong>.<br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1699\" height=\"751\" class=\"wp-image-570\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/customize123.jpg\" alt=\"Accessing the customize page on Shopify admin\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/customize123.jpg 1699w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/customize123-600x265.jpg 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/customize123-1200x530.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/customize123-768x339.jpg 768w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/customize123-1536x679.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1699px) 100vw, 1699px\" /></li><li>On the top, from the dropdown options, select <strong>product pages</strong>. <br><br>Once this page loads, click on <strong>product pages</strong> on the left.<br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"804\" height=\"485\" class=\"wp-image-632\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/prod1.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/prod1.jpg 804w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/prod1-600x362.jpg 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/prod1-768x463.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 804px) 100vw, 804px\" /></li><li>Inside the <strong>Product pages</strong> menu you&#8217;ll find all available options for the Minimal Slider.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<h3>Something went wrong, there is a bug or I can&#8217;t install it</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>No worries at all! We&#8217;ll be more than happy to help you out. <br><br>Just please send us an email at <strong>ezfycode@gmail</strong> with your website URL and we&#8217;ll get back to you on the same day to assist you and get it installed.</p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Learn how to add a rich slideshow to your product pages in just a few minutes. More than 20 customizable features built-in.</p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":637,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[9],"tags":[154,243,82],"image_alt":"","acf":[],"featured_image_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/MinimalSlider-600x338.png","featured_image_small_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/MinimalSlider-100x100.png","post_count":0,"categories_names":["Blog"],"tag_names":["Code Tutorial","Minimal Theme","product page"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/618"}],"collection":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/types/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/users/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/comments?post=618"}],"version-history":[{"count":10,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/618/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":653,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/618/revisions/653"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/media/637"}],"wp:att